Turning these two css settings off improved the UI/UX of the blog a thousand times:pre {
    margin: 2rem 0 !important;
    padding: 1rem !important;
}Each code block has such giant padding and margins that you can only read 3 lines of text in a viewport.Also, I would suggest installing Webmin/Virtualmin which takes care of a lot of issues like deploying new subdomains or new users.
